snippet.textDisplay: There was this one girl in school who was Saddle Club crazy. One day there was some competition thing in class. I think it was like year 6 or something. Anyway, there was a range of prizes you could win. The first person got to select from all the prizes, and so on and so forth. The last person got what was left. You know how it goes. Anyway, there were the Saddle Club pencils. The teacher obviously put them i there knowing that only one person in the class would pick them, that being the Saddle Club crazy girl. However, this one kid got to pick from the pile of prizes before she did. He took the pencils and then promptly snapped them in half in front of the class. Lets just say he got detention, and the Saddle Club girl got mad and ran out balling her eyes out. It was a pretty shit thing for that go to have done.

snippet.textDisplay:
Horse girl story:
My schools horse girl was in one of my classes. My friend liked to make fun of her pretty much constantly. One day he decides to say very loudly “Man, I’m so hungry I could eat a horse.”
Horse girl becomes very angry.
Horse girl starts to yell.
“HORSE SLAUGHTER IS ILLEGAL IN THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA”
My friend is laughing. Horse girl only gets angrier.
“YOU CANNOT EAT A HORSE IT IS ILLEGALLLLL”

P.S: “Horse” doesn’t sound like a word anymore
